	<h1 class="title">动动鼠标就能泄露情绪？这份研究说：就是这样</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/43366/small/43366.jpg?1430896699" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王民超 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-15 14:12:24 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19100/medium/19100.jpg?1450158036" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="19100" data-title="《动动鼠标就能泄露情绪？这份研究说：就是这样》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/19100/medium/19100.jpg?1450158036" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/19100.html?from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=1" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
